            <title>[FLINK-20486] Hive temporal join should allow monitor interval smaller than 1 hour</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-20486</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently hive temporal join requires the monitor interval to be at least 1h, which may not fit everyone&apos;s needs. Although we recommend a relatively large monitor interval, we shouldn&apos;t make such decision for users. A warning log is a better option for a small interval.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
